Hover hand
[[File:Hover hand 8.jpg|center|frame| That awkward smile would turn to a vicious snarl should the hand actually touch]]
Hot [[wimmenz]] can be very repulsed by kissless virgins such as [[you]]rself. The '''Hover hand''' is an example of the pitiful nerd's [[socially awkward]] behavior: a coping mechanism for their hopeless desire to interact with a society that despises and oppresses them.  The motivation behind the hover hand may be a fear of breaching perceived social boundaries, or violation of the friend zone protocols; however it is more likely that they realize that their [[Fat|overweight]] bodies, [[Otaku|socially awkward manner]], [[Goofy Time|deep psychological issues]], strong 'I haven't bathed in a month' smell, obvious [[Virgin|virginity]], greasy [[neckbeard|neckbeards]] and [[FAIL|failures]] in [[Life|life]] are about as appealing to a woman as having [[RAPE|sex with a nigger]]. The fact is, if you touch them they would call the [[cops]]. This [[autistic|retarded]] behavior is a physical demonstration of how basement dwellers are doomed to be [[forever alone]]. 

'''The [[white knight|moral]]:''' women think you're creepy.  Stay in your fucking basement.
